OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782379108
OL,3,CSchool sets up classroom 'cool spot'
OL,4,Cto help pupils struggling in extreme
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,FA school in New Alresford in Hampshire
OL,8,Fhas set up a dedicated "cool spot" for
OL,9,Fpupils who are struggling in the
OL,10,Fextreme heat.
OL,12,FPerins School has remained open this
OL,13,Fweek and has adapted the classroom for
OL,14,Fchildren, introducing special measures
OL,15,Fto help keep children cool.
OL,17,FThis week is expected to be the
OL,18,Fhottest on record, with temperatures
OL,19,Fof up to 40C on Wednesday and Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
