OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782379108
OL,3,CSchool sets up classroom 'cool spot'
OL,4,Cto help pupils struggling in extreme
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,FRare red weather warnings are in place
OL,8,Ffor parts of the south of England.
OL,10,FThe latest heatwave is expected to
OL,11,Fsurpass the record for June of 35.6C
OL,12,Fset in Hampshire in 1976.
OL,14,FHeadteacher of Perins School Mark
OL,15,FNevola, said they have introduced
OL,16,Ftimetable changes with a shorter
OL,17,Fschool day, as well as a dedicated
OL,18,Fcold spot for youngsters who may feel
OL,19,Fadverse effects of the heat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782379108
OL,3,CSchool sets up classroom 'cool spot'
OL,4,Cto help pupils struggling in extreme
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,F"We've put an air conditioning unit in
OL,8,Fand allowed lots of water for those
OL,9,Fyoungsters," he said.
OL,11,F"We've allowed them to come in PE kit
OL,12,Fand obviously the staff have been
OL,13,Fgiving messages on a regular basis and
OL,14,FI've been messaging home to ensure
OL,15,Fthey have sunscreen,hats and plenty of
OL,16,Fwater and refillable water bottles."
OL,18,FMany schools have closed, or partially
OL,19,Fclosed over the two days of extreme
OL,20,Fheat, which has prompted criticism
OL,21,Ffrom some claiming it's not necessary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782379108
OL,3,CSchool sets up classroom 'cool spot'
OL,4,Cto help pupils struggling in extreme
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,FBut Mr Nevola said with increasing
OL,8,Ftemperatures, schools have to adapt
OL,9,Ffor the future.
OL,11,F"It may well be that schools have to
OL,12,Flook at the curriculum in the future,
OL,13,Fhave a look at the school day and
OL,14,Fadapt accordingly," he added.
OL,16,F"We've tried to educate students about
OL,17,Fheat stroke, so if they're getting to
OL,18,Fa point where they need a cool room,
OL,19,Fthen a cold spot's been created.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
