FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782379108
OL,3,CSchool sets up classroom 'cool spot'
OL,4,Cto help pupils struggling in extreme
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,FPublic Health England has issued
OL,8,Fguidance on how to stay cool during
OL,9,Fthe extreme heat.
OL,11,FPeople should avoid being outside
OL,12,Fduring the hottest hours (11am - 3pm),
OL,13,Fdrink lots of water, regularly apply
OL,14,Fsun cream and wear a wide-brimmed hat
OL,15,Fand light-coloured, loose clothing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
